    <item>
      <title>中国誓言动员全国对抗美国科技霸主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-vows-to-mobilize-nation-as-it-fights-us-for-tech-supremacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国承诺利用全国资源加速本土科学突破，并重申在人工智能、芯片制造等领域实现自力更生，从美国手中夺取技术霸主地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-vows-to-mobilize-nation-as-it-fights-us-for-tech-supremacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:41:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平加强国防建设，中国国防开支将增长 7.2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-defense-spending-to-climb-7-2-as-xi-pursues-buildup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024年中国国防开支将增长7.2%——五年来最多——有迹象表明，腐败正在破坏军事改革，而这一数字却在增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-defense-spending-to-climb-7-2-as-xi-pursues-buildup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:42:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国计划发行1390亿美元的特别超长期债务以促进经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-unveils-139-billion-in-special-central-debt-for-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着当局加大对世界第二大经济体的财政刺激力度，中国计划今年发行1万亿元人民币（1390亿美元）的超长期特别中央政府债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-unveils-139-billion-in-special-central-debt-for-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在国内拒绝乌克兰外交官，破坏和平进程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-spurns-ukraine-diplomats-at-home-undermining-peace-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已派出一名高级外交官前往基辅寻求政治解决战争问题。但在北京内部，乌克兰外交官似乎受到冷遇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-spurns-ukraine-diplomats-at-home-undermining-peace-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国发现哈马斯自 10 月 7 日以来实施性暴力的证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/un-cites-evidence-hamas-committed-sexual-violence-since-oct-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国找到了“合理的理由”得出结论，哈马斯在 10 月 7 日袭击以色列期间实施了性暴力，并表示有迹象表明此类暴力行为仍在继续针对被该组织扣为人质的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/un-cites-evidence-hamas-committed-sexual-violence-since-oct-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国资助协议对司法部对苹果、Ticketmaster 的反垄断调查造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-funding-deal-delivers-blow-to-doj-antitrust-probes-of-apple-ticketmaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项让联邦政府在 9 月份保持运转的支出协议将限制反垄断执法机构可获得的资金，这可能会阻碍对苹果公司和 Live Nation Entertainment Inc. 旗下 Ticketmaster 的高调调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-funding-deal-delivers-blow-to-doj-antitrust-probes-of-apple-ticketmaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:31:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦总理下令与国际货币基金组织开始贷款谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/pakistan-pm-sharif-orders-starting-talks-with-imf-for-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦总理谢巴兹·谢里夫指示当局加快与国际货币基金组织的谈判，该国 30 亿美元的救助计划将于 4 月结束。]]></description>
